NAME
    Crypt::Caesar - Decrypt rot-N strings

INSTALLATION

    To install this module type the following:

        perl Makefile.PL
        make
        make test
        make install

SYNOPSIS
        use Crypt::Caesar;
        print caesar("Vn tjp xvi nzz, do rjmfn.\n");

DESCRIPTION
    This module is based on the caesar program from the bsdgames package,
    made by Stan King and John Eldridge, based on the algorithm suggested by
    Bob Morris.

  "caesar"
    This is the only function this package provides. It is exported by
    default and prototyped ($).

AUTHOR
    Juerd

